{"TopicId":180058,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Player achievements!","CreatedByName":"Astrodym","CreatedById":190759,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-24T23:40:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Astrodym","CreatedById":190759,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-24T23:40:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey ya\u0027ll, you\u0027ve probably seen this come up before, but I find myself thinking\u00A0once I\u0027ve landed a probe on a distant planet, or landed the eagle on the Mun - \u0022Why did I do this?\u0022 and the answer has always been\u00A0\u0022Because I can\u0022. If there was an achievement system, it might\u00A0give the player a sense of accomplishment (even if they\u0027ve done something insane already) and pride for their space program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust wanted to hear your thoughts on this.\u00A0\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T03:46:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forums.\u00A0\u00A0 There are achievements in game, at least in career mode.\u00A0 You can earn world firsts.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 But achievements tend to stifle creativity in my opinion.\u00A0\u00A0 If you give players a list of things to accomplish, then they will often only accomplish those things.\u00A0\u00A0 The free form nature of KSP is what lends it self to the explorations we do for our own personal achievement.\u00A0\u00A0 And bragging rights here on the forums.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T03:58:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA very very long time ago, before there was even a career mode, there was a mod called Achievements.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2731395015\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/48225-0242-achievements-163-earn-136-achievements-while-playing/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt faded away when career mode took over that aspect of the game but I quite liked it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile looking for that, I found this mod, which is current. I have no experience with it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4145285772\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/164965-15-space-age-101-2018-10-17-tracking-your-achievements-and-failures-since-year-1-day-1/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T04:02:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinal frontier is another good one in that vein, VHM.\u00A0\u00A0 Instead of player achievements, it tracks individual Kerbal achievements.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T17:28:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223493205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543118520\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinal frontier is another good one in that vein, VHM.\u00A0\u00A0 Instead of player achievements, it tracks individual Kerbal achievements.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s an achievement system that fits into the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOtherwise, go get \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.amazon.com/ChromaLabel-Color-Code-Labels-Dispenser-Metallic/dp/B00PM3D2WI/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethis\u003C/a\u003E, and every time you do something, peel one off, stick it somewhere, and feel good about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"roboslacker","CreatedById":175473,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T17:38:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoesn\u0027t the console edition have achievements?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-25T18:41:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223493463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543167488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175473\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022roboslacker\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, roboslacker said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoesn\u0027t the console edition have achievements?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.trueachievements.com/game/Kerbal-Space-Program/achievements\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.trueachievements.com/game/Kerbal-Space-Program/achievements\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DerekL1963","CreatedById":57091,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T19:13:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223493196\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543117579\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/24/2018 at 7:46 PM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut achievements tend to stifle creativity in my opinion.\u00A0\u00A0 If you give players a list of things to accomplish, then they will often only accomplish those things.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nPretty much this.\u00A0 Give players a list of ticky boxes to tick off - and they\u0027ll soon see that as the only\u00A0\u0022right and proper\u0022 way to play the game.\u00A0 (Due to the conditioning from other games where progress/ability to \u0022win\u0022 is linked to achievements.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T19:31:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinal Frontier.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed982009490\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/61065-151-final-frontier-kerbal-individual-merits-150-3380/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat mod with plenty of customization options. Doesn\u0027t take much (if any) processing power either.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T21:04:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223493196\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543117579\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/24/2018 at 10:46 PM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eachievements tend to stifle creativity in my opinion\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile I can\u0027t disagree with that statement, I would like to add that they don\u0027t have to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother of my favorite games, Factorio, has several achievements that encourage a player outside their comfort zone. And one, whose name would probably be filtered here but has \u0022Lazy\u0022 on the name, is actually the reason I played it for hundreds of hours instead of dozens. It got me to try a methodology that I didn\u0027t think I\u0027d take to, that became the only way I wanted to play the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T21:08:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223494243\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543266278\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFactorio\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen that on sale before, is it actually a good game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T21:24:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223494246\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543266482\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen that on sale before, is it actually a good game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s fantastic. It shares the top 10 all-time favorite list with KSP. May even be top 5.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you like math and efficiency and automation and optimization, give it a look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-26T21:27:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223494251\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543267453\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s fantastic. It shares the top 10 all-time favorite list with KSP. May even be top 5.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you like math and efficiency and automation and optimization, give it a look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks. The next time I see it on sale, I will buy it...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}